    "description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索城市<br>在大城市中自由漫游，乘坐公共交通工具，探索公园、街道和新地点。每个角落都邀请你体验新的冒险。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras/9ca252acc67e4936ddfda90a523d4e7c.avif?t=1741448206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras_big/9ca252acc67e4936ddfda90a523d4e7c.avif?t=1741448206 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创建你的风格<br>在服装店中选择你的风格，在理发店修剪发型和胡须，在健身房保持身材。为自己打造一个独特的造型。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras/163293b9f13b08aeacee56f599dd3f04.avif?t=1741448206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras_big/163293b9f13b08aeacee56f599dd3f04.avif?t=1741448206 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras/48e5a4a89488b7e2c29bcfde16246f3e.avif?t=1741448206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras_big/48e5a4a89488b7e2c29bcfde16246f3e.avif?t=1741448206 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras/38b4ddf7f26d8b8e86f0dd0762dcf8fd.avif?t=1741448206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras_big/38b4ddf7f26d8b8e86f0dd0762dcf8fd.avif?t=1741448206 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >豪华生活<br>随着财富的增长，打造你梦想中的豪华生活方式。通过时尚的汽车和豪华的住宅提升你的生活标准。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras/6a7a92002484ecefc9285e2ed99c482c.avif?t=1741448206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras_big/6a7a92002484ecefc9285e2ed99c482c.avif?t=1741448206 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >社交生活<br>与女性认识，在夜店中玩乐，社交生活中的每一刻都将带给你新的体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras/e0eb41c1f07f4fb0e4971b5eb6b8d4d6.avif?t=1741448206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras_big/e0eb41c1f07f4fb0e4971b5eb6b8d4d6.avif?t=1741448206 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras/b26e2f87500f218edfdd8c9da8c41ef1.avif?t=1741448206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras_big/b26e2f87500f218edfdd8c9da8c41ef1.avif?t=1741448206 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各种工作机会<br>通过不同的工作赚取收入。作为公交车司机、服务员或超市员工，一边探索城市一边赚钱。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras/2064a25862bba945a269375322ed511d.avif?t=1741448206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras_big/2064a25862bba945a269375322ed511d.avif?t=1741448206 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras/b0142ecf3847ed3f3ac55c247274bc9c.avif?t=1741448206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318000/extras_big/b0142ecf3847ed3f3ac55c247274bc9c.avif?t=1741448206 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/33180